==Chinese==
===[[Mandarin]]===
[[Pinyin]]: bù dǎ bù xiāngshì 

===Proverb===
'''[[不]][[打]][[不]][[相識]]'''
# Friends are often made after a fight; from an exchange of blows friendship grows; no acquaintance is made without a fight; no discord, no concord; out of blows friendship grows.

===Alternate forms===
